The paper discusses the challenge of software citation in scientific and engineering research, which is a topic that falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses metadata necessary for software citation, which is related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also touches on issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and databases (cs.DB) as they relate to software reuse and identification.
